about.summary: Iconic fonts in PyQt and PySide applications

name: qtawesome
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.3.3" %}
{% set sha256 = "c3c98ee4df0133ae42d202fea20253f8746266b4541c5df4269ca4131792ce0f" %}

package:
    name: qtawesome
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: qtawesome-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/q/qtawesome/QtAwesome-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - six
        - python
        - qtpy

test:
    requires:
        - pyqt
    imports:
        - qtawesome

about:
    home: https://github.com/spyder-ide/qtawesome
    license: MIT
    summary: Iconic fonts in PyQt and PySide applications

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - SylvainCorlay
        - goanpeca
        - ccordoba12
